a.title: ― Code: The characters used as a symbol to designate a category within a codelist or classification. (Formally, a sign for which the signifier is non-linguistic alphanumeric string.)

a.title: ― Notation: Representation of a category in the context of a code or a classification item, as opposed of the corresponding instance value which would appear when used in a dataset.
